I"w<p>Deception Royale is a <strong>2D top-down multiplayer battle royale</strong> game, where each player tries to remain the last one standing. Up to 20 people can connect to a match and play against each other. The game was made as an entry to the <a href="https://itch.io/jam/2nd-winter-game-jam">2nd AAU Winter Game Jam</a>.</p>

<p>The game was built using the <strong>Unity3D</strong> engine and written in <strong>C#</strong>. I worked in a team of two on this, as a <strong>gameplay programme</strong>r. A mini-map functionality was also added programmed by me. For the multiplayer, we used Unity’s <strong>UNet API</strong>.</p>

